{"tid":1793423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請聲援林手足，林手足不是condom，不要忘記他","createTime":"2019-12-22T11:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T11:31:35.000Z","uid":280899,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e825472dc668a36d846ee52951cfbe8e0b79d552","tid":1793423,"uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T11:30:16.000Z","msg":"他，朝早走在前線屌月娥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n他，晚上在床上堅屌月娥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n他，日以繼晚，夜以繼日屌左月娥三十幾個春秋<br />\n除左習大大，佢應該係屌得月娥次數最多的人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早兩日，林手足仲要用攬炒的態度，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狠狠地車左習曱甴好多巴，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫香港人出左一口氣，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以林手足不是condom</span></strong>，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請求各位手足舉行聲援林手足，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等佢知道，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">他不是condom</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就算佢老婆係月娥，我地都唔會割席!</span><br />\nwe are connected !<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不分化<br />\n不割席<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"a99a3f2add3ad31dd52c5146d0a94fd79d4a778c","tid":1793423,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T11:31:35.000Z","msg":"【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【置頂】【行動po求推】好㷫呀！警曱向人群舉槍，聽日同我即刻行動。而嚟緊嘅行動係1223stuck稅局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793389</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【行動po】【求推】點解1223去稅局 連登冇人講？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1792093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1792093</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n點解1223稅局冇人提？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1781990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1781990</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FbPAwwX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFbPAwwX.jpg&h=af432327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WvBryAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWvBryAY.jpg&h=fea3e57a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7grryiG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7grryiG.jpg&h=5fde20aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddDxvuv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FddDxvuv.jpg&h=525dd049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&